{"tid":932151,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"不得不說《悲傷》呢套戲都幾戇鳩","createTime":"2018-12-07T13:45:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-07T17:44:39.000Z","uid":39264,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5697a6c8feb3ff139bab5b7fc0fb77e583c210fe","tid":932151,"uid":39264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T13:45:10.000Z","msg":"呢套戲最悲傷嘅人根本上就係個牙醫<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你老味做咗場大龍鳳呃鳩撚左結婚<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n女角之後是但講兩句就搵返男主角<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 最撚過癮嘅係 原來女角一早知道男主角就死<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n為咗唔想令到男主角傷心竟然順着男主角安排俾佢嘅計劃 同牙醫結婚<br />\n<br />\n台妹真係善用自己身體成就事情<br />\n（包括牙醫條ex ，綠帽左人哋六年；但牙醫本身自己都戇鳩，俾人綠帽左6年都唔知）<br />\n<br />\n咁你最後就唔好搵返男主角啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後仲要殉情<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n台狗真係戇鳩"},{"pid":"03a17369b197b5dd4939c349e126ffb8a85986fb","tid":932151,"uid":45479,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T15:14:17.000Z","msg":"佢真係好撚慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 每一段關係都俾人呃緊"},{"pid":"116d8f1ad0d86019933a5bd73207633017bec6d5","tid":932151,"uid":167810,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T17:25:12.000Z","msg":"睇完都覺得膠膠地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n網上吹奏話好sad好好睇"},{"pid":"5489997d2747e8e6cbbe625ef7449c7b30df1f20","tid":932151,"uid":149435,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T17:44:39.000Z","msg":"其實係翻拍韓國電影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}